      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>Create a PxrOSL VOP Node (note the operator name is pxrosl:2 to avoid clashing with the node shipped with Houdini).</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"394\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644451/rfh_PxrOSL.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433128218&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=394&amp;height=561\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644451/rfh_PxrOSL.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433128218&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"964\" data-width=\"676\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644469\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfh_PxrOSL.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644451\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"e736f0e0-dff4-4120-8682-936881563900\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644451/rfh_PxrOSL.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433128218&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=676&amp;height=964 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644451/rfh_PxrOSL.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433128218&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=394&amp;height=561 1x\"></span><ul><li><p>File Path for the oso. Parameters and inputs loaded from this oso</p></li><li><p>Source File Path for the osl. Will be compiled to File Path</p></li><li><p>Compose osl in code block. </p></li></ul><p>Set RMAN_SHADERPATH environment variable to load oso files in path. These will be organized in TAB menu based on directory levels where they are saved. </p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"8a4a4f1f-7d6c-4064-ae3e-2aac947b69ba\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">Set environment variable RFH_ARGS2HDA=1 to create houdini digital assets on start up based on .args or .oso files found in RMAN_SHADERPATH and/or RMAN_RIXPLUGINPATH.</span></p></div></div><ul><li><p>.oso shaders found in $RMAN_SHADERPATH are automatically converted to otls, and stored in $HOUDINI_USER_PREF_DIR/otls/rfh_osllib.hda</p></li></ul>"
    }
